data.title: The Devil's Mistress
data.meta_description: The Devil's Mistress (2016) starring Tatiana Pauhofová, Karl Markovics, Gedeon Burkhard and directed by Filip Renč.
data.text: Salzburg, Germany, 2000. The elderly Czech actress Lída Baarová tells a journalist the tumultuous story of her rise to fame in 1930s Berlin and her passionate relationship with the sinister Joseph Goebbels, Minister of Propaganda of the Third Reich.
